data.description: This quality constructed home from 2008 has never been lived in and has been completely remodeled from top to bottom. Featuring an amazing floor plan with an open concept. The kitchen boasts brand new stainless steel appliances with granite countertops and new cabinets. The center island has extra storage space as well as a place for bar stools for extra seating. This 3 bedroom home offers a split plan with a large master bedroom. All bedrooms include a closet system with custom wood shelving in the master closet. Contemporary barn doors throughout the home with matching crown molding and floor trim. Two full baths, both brand new, with the master bath topped off with a beautifully tiled walk in shower, double sinks and contemporary lighting. Enjoy the newly constructed custom front deck with stairway on the warm summer days with plenty of seating area. Paved parking for up to six vehicles behind home. This gem has all of the finishing touches to make your next home the perfect choice. A Honeywell heating system and Ring security system with flood lighting is included as well as the stackable washer and dryer in the separate laundry closet. Close to schools, freeways and shopping as well as downtown Knoxville with its many restaurants and attractions. Come see this home today before it's too late. Buyer to verify all information.
